messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签应为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "label_mapping",
          "detail": "INTENT_MAPPING 未将 raw_intent='4001' 映射到 customer_portrait，回退为 other"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "detail": "提取时未正确传递原始意图编码，直接输出 other"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "label_mapping 中缺乏从意图模型原始编码 4001 到 customer_portrait 的映射配置，导致最终意图错误为 other；adapter_extraction 未能向下传递原始编码，加剧问题。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "value": {
            "intent": "other"
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_evidence",
          "value": {
            "raw_intent": "4001"
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "runtime_checks",
          "value": "raw_intent=None 映射到 other（实际 raw_intent=4001 但映射失败）"
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_contract_probe",
          "value": {
            "intent_match": false,
            "evidence_intent": "4001"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "目标实体应为重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "detail": "意图模型未返回任何目标实体"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "detail": "未从 API 响应中提取出实体 target_value"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图模型未能从用户查询中抽取“重疾险”作为目标实体，可能因模型训练或 prompt 设计未覆盖该实体类型；adapter_extraction 也未填充 target_value。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "value": {
            "target_value": null
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_evidence",
          "value": {
            "entities": [],
            "slots": {}
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "reference_contract",
          "value": {
            "target_value": "重疾险"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度至少为0.9",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "detail": "模型返回置信度 0.5，远低于期望"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图模型对类似“查询客户画像”的意图识别置信度低下，表明模型分类边界模糊或训练数据不足，导致无法提供高置信度。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "value": {
            "confidence": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "reference_contract",
          "value": {
            "confidence": 0.95
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_contract_probe",
          "value": {
            "actual_confidence": 0.5
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "不应错误触发fallback意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "label_mapping",
          "detail": "映射为 other 等同于 fallback 行为"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于主体意图被错误映射为 other，实际上触发了 fallback 的处理路径，违背了不应将有效查询归为 other 的预期。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "value": {
            "intent": "other"
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_evidence",
          "value": {
            "fallback": false
          }
        },
        {
          "source": "judge_result",
          "value": "不应将明确业务查询归类为 other"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "label_mapping",
      "detail": "映射表缺失 raw_intent=4001 的映射"
    },
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "detail": "提取意图逻辑可能丢失原始编码或错误提取"
    },
    {
      "stage": "intent_api_call",
      "detail": "模型未提取目标实体且置信度过低"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在 marketing-planning-intent 项目的单轮意图识别链路中，label_mapping 阶段未能将意图模型输出的原始编码 '4001' 映射到期望意图 'customer_portrait'，导致意图降级为 'other'；adapter_extraction 阶段也可能未正确保留原始编码信息。同时，意图模型未提取关键实体 '重疾险'，且返回的置信度仅为 0.5，低于预期 0.9。综合以上映射配置缺失、模型提取能力不足和置信度偏低，导致所有业务期望未达成。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "source": "reference_contract",
      "value": {
        "intent": "customer_portrait",
        "target_value": "重疾险",
        "confidence": 0.95
      }
    },
    {
      "source": "extracted_output",
      "value": {
        "intent": "other",
        "confidence": 0.5,
        "target_value": null
      }
    },
    {
      "source": "intent_evidence",
      "value": {
        "raw_intent": "4001",
        "entities": [],
        "slots": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "source": "intent_contract_probe",
      "value": {
        "intent_match": false,
        "evidence_intent": "4001"
      }
    },
    {
      "source": "runtime_checks",
      "value": {
        "status": "failed",
        "root_cause": "raw_intent=None 映射到 other",
        "mapping_source": "INTENT_MAPPING"
      }
    },
    {
      "source": "judge_result",
      "value": {
        "overall_fulfillment": "not_fulfilled",
        "blocking_expectations": ["intent_contract"]
      }
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

